window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A three-in-one collection featuring previously released titles: <i>Dreams of Darkness</i>, <i>Awake in Shadows</i>, and <i>Kiss of Light</i>.</p> <p>Adara has no idea who she is.</p> <p>What she is.</p> <p>That doesn't stop danger from stalking her.</p> <p>It also does nothing to stem the nightmares.</p> <p>Caught in her dreams of darkness, Adara attracts the attention of a werewolf and a vampire and wonders if she's losing her mind. They can't exist, and her mind says forget. But she wants to remember. However, if she does, will the truth shatter her?</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
